Pearl Harbor?

10
00:02:22,476 --> 00:02:24,979
(explosions booming)

11
00:02:25,187 --> 00:02:26,522
Is that why we are fighting?

12
00:02:27,732 --> 00:02:28,649
Or is it because of

13
00:02:28,858 --> 00:02:30,401
(explosions booming)

14
00:02:30,610 --> 00:02:31,736
Britain?

15
00:02:31,944 --> 00:02:34,905
(explosions booming)

16
