19
00:03:01,724 --> 00:03:02,433
China?

20
00:03:02,642 --> 00:03:04,518
(plane engines humming)

21
00:03:06,937 --> 00:03:09,357
(explosions booming)

22
00:03:09,565 --> 00:03:10,232
Czechoslovakia?

23
00:03:13,152 --> 00:03:15,112
(explosions booming)

24
00:03:15,321 --> 00:03:16,030
Norway?

25
00:03:17,323 --> 00:03:20,034
(plane engines humming)

26
00:03:21,952 --> 00:03:24,038
(explosions booming)

27
00:03:24,246 --> 00:03:24,872
(plane screeching)

28
00:03:25,081 --> 00:03:26,582
Poland?

29
